  "title": "Operator (Aerospace)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Perform manual and mechanical deburring on metallic and/or composite aerospace components.</li><li>Use hand tools, power tools, abrasive media, files, grinders, and polishing equipment as required.</li><li>Identify and report non-conformances, defects, or damage to supervisors or quality personnel.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>GCE O level and above</li><li>Experience working in an<strong> aerospace or precision manufacturing environment.</strong></li><li>Strong attention to detail and quality awareness.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
